<ul>
<li>访问阿里云百炼页面并登录账号 https://www.aliyun.com/product/bailian</li>
</ul>
<p><img src="@source/17-AI 与智能应用/Spring AI/课件/image/image-20250516020053364.png" alt="image-20250516020053364"></p>
<ul>
<li>开通“百炼大模型推理”服务，获取API Key。</li>
</ul>
